How to create a list of books:

```sql
select BookId from libseq where seqid IN 
(63460, 81208, 85274, 79232, 80578, 56313, 60679, 76921, 59890, 70621, 34145, 40913, 64912, 66568, 47136, 38139, 52589);
```
